This repo is a simple vpi framework using c/c++ code for RTL simulation to abstract the hardware simulation. 

The simulation environment compiles verilog code with iverilog, and gtkwave to visulaize the waveform. 

* Note : When compiling the cpp files using "iverilog-vpi", the first argument should be the major registration function (e.g. register.cpp), then the other cpp files.

(iverilog-vpi register.cpp module.cpp tiling.cpp)
